  "body": "[get_shard_committees_at_slot](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/master/specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md#get_shard_committees_at_slot) value for `slot - earliest_slot_in_array` can be below zero in `return state.shard_committees_at_slots[slot - earliest_slot_in_array]`\r\n\r\nI suggest the addition of `return state.shard_committees_at_slots[max(slot, slot - earliest_slot_in_array)]` to keep the value from passing below 0.\r\n",
